    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Embark on a journey, freely exploring a vast and breathtaking world</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ancient landscapes of YARETA seem frozen in time, with towering mountains and strange, vibrant creatures and plants thriving in peaceful isolation. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/89c561df358975de5bb6739825fe4b82.poster.avif?t=1771333207\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/89c561df358975de5bb6739825fe4b82.webm?t=1771333207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/89c561df358975de5bb6739825fe4b82.mp4?t=1771333207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Encounter majestic, awe-inspiring creatures</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world’s rich ecosystems hold countless surprises, with unexpected interactions unfolding as you meet the land’s fantastic creatures.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/1c481a6795a24239728f2a5c12a645f2.poster.avif?t=1771333207\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/1c481a6795a24239728f2a5c12a645f2.webm?t=1771333207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/1c481a6795a24239728f2a5c12a645f2.mp4?t=1771333207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Connect to the Sky Rope and take in the beauty of the world</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beyond traveling on foot, your unique ability to glide with the Sky Rope lets you experience the land’s beauty from an entirely new perspective. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/482cee724d09b7582613983eb2aef4b7.poster.avif?t=1771333207\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/482cee724d09b7582613983eb2aef4b7.webm?t=1771333207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/482cee724d09b7582613983eb2aef4b7.mp4?t=1771333207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Interact with the world and let your curiosity guide you</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brave the unknown, following the mysteries of the land as you uncover secrets hidden within the ancient world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/dcc9250dc19813587c6d8dd6e0b6913a.poster.avif?t=1771333207\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/dcc9250dc19813587c6d8dd6e0b6913a.webm?t=1771333207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/dcc9250dc19813587c6d8dd6e0b6913a.mp4?t=1771333207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Engage with nature, creating endless possibilities</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experiment with the world around you, using its natural wonders to unlock new paths and opportunities in your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/f7150afe7a2a5f884a6a19a1d3a7faec.poster.avif?t=1771333207\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/f7150afe7a2a5f884a6a19a1d3a7faec.webm?t=1771333207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/f7150afe7a2a5f884a6a19a1d3a7faec.mp4?t=1771333207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Uncover the mystery of your origins</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What truths lie hidden within these ancient ruins? Explore the forgotten past and unravel the enigma of your own story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/315a002c36e4fa11240380510fcf243e.poster.avif?t=1771333207\" width=500 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/315a002c36e4fa11240380510fcf243e.webm?t=1771333207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230380/extras/315a002c36e4fa11240380510fcf243e.mp4?t=1771333207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
